			<div class="content" id="post-content-3748519">
									

<p>Here's a tale I've been drafting over the last couple months. If this goes well, expect a part 2, focusing on the more modern Animal Assets Division.</p>
<p>Thanks to:<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1404533); return false;">Zyn</a></span> for looking over my very first draft and suggesting structural changes.<br />
<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2150500); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2150500&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="LadyKatie" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2150500)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ladykatie" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2150500); return false;">LadyKatie</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/baseplate-actual" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3762904); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3762904&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="Baseplate-Actual" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3762904)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/baseplate-actual" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3762904); return false;">Baseplate-Actual</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/draycott" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3737554); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3737554&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="Draycott" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3737554)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/draycott" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3737554); return false;">Draycott</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/recursiverecursion" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1864349); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1864349&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="RecursiveRecursion" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1864349)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/recursiverecursion" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1864349); return false;">RecursiveRecursion</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2198340); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2198340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="Kakroom" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2198340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kakroom" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2198340); return false;">Kakroom</a></span> for giving it a read over in chat, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimmcreeper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2843467); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2843467&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="GrimmCreeper" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2843467)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/grimmcreeper" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2843467); return false;">GrimmCreeper</a></span>,<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3009022&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1521918878" alt="not_a_seagull" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3009022)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/not-a-seagull" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3009022); return false;">not_a_seagull</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/solarrose" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3775444); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3775444&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;t