						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,3749683)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ratsy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3050018); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3050018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227467" alt="ratsy" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3050018)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ratsy" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3050018); return false;" >ratsy</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1522023665 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">26 Mar 2018 00:21</span>
